 at kommunen havner i kattepina. Ikke sparer de penger og grenda splittes.", "Men det er likevel umulig \u00e5 klandre foreldrene. Det f\u00f8lger ofte et engasjement rundt de private skolene som den offentlige skolen bare kan dr\u00f8mme om."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "3e940d06b007032aa0bc59ca3b0f02b821b75a509da092efd5b2a4f65e74cd1a"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-19T16:17:01.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Engasjerte foreldre kan ikke klandres for \u00e5 redde grendeskolen. Men for kommunen betyr det tr\u00f8bbel."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/article10062551.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/JPS_meldalskole27.JPG"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/b9498360bf71dcfd7b176edabdcf0d6711611a56.jpg?58ceaefd"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Kommunal kattepine -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "b9498360bf71dcfd7b176edabdcf0d6711611a56"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["pluss", "eadressa", "ukeadressa", "digitalt", "arkiv", "fordeler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "pluss,eadressa,ukeadressa,digitalt,arkiv,fordeler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["pedagogisk alternativ", "kommunen", "skole"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["montessori", "l\u00f8kken", "steinerskolen", "f\u00f8niks"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "meldal"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/article10062551.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/JPS_meldalskole27.JPG"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Kommunal kattepine"}, {"field": "og-type", "value"